thread.title: Valerie

author: Valerie
title: Valerie
text: I have recently bought a iPhone 7 so I also bought this case from casetify (the last one broke because I dropped it on the ground). This time, I have dropped it for several times and the phone is still perfectly fine! Despite a minor issue of delayed delivery (but someone at casetify got back to me quickly on their Facebook page after I left a message), overall I am very happy with my case! Can't wait to buy more. :D
